tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  funding_amount DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  start_date DATE NOT NULL,
  end_date DATE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    funding_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE project_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    report_description TEXT,
    impact_rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE funded_projects (
  project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  funding_amount DECIMAL,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE project_reports (
  report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  report_date DATE,
  report_content TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE project_impact (
  impact_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id INT,
  impact_description TEXT,
  impact_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE projects (
    project_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_name VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    funding_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE project_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    member_name VARCHAR(255),
    role VARCHAR(50),
    JOIN TABLE projects(project_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE project_activities (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    activity_description TEXT,
    activity_date DATE,
    JOIN TABLE projects(project_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE project_impact_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    impact_description TEXT,
    JOIN TABLE projects(project_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE funded_projects (
  project_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_name VARCHAR(255),
  funding_source VARCHAR(255),
  funding_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE project_expenses (
  expense_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id UUID REFERENCES funded_projects(project_id),
  expense_description TEXT,
  expense_amount DECIMAL(10, 2),
  expense_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE project_activities (
  activity_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id UUID REFERENCES funded_projects(project_id),
  activity_name VARCHAR(255),
  activity_date DATE,
  activity_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE project_participants (
  participant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id UUID REFERENCES funded_projects(project_id),
  participant_name VARCHAR(255),
  participant_role VARCHAR(50),
  participant_contact VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE project_reports (
  report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  project_id UUID REFERENCES funded_projects(project_id),
  report_date DATE,
  report_description TEXT
)
